link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.collaction.hk%2Fproject%2Fstory%2F1209&d=1ryX%2BwltUSTIgmnFzyWg%2BJbpPLVkgxcsq72qYZiHPFQ%3D&h=385abd4a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209</a><br />\n官方link (我們香港人計劃) :<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.pori.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pori.hk%2F&d=1ryX%2BwltUSTIgmnFzyWg%2BJbpPLVkgxcsq72qYZiHPFQ%3D&h=764e68df\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.pori.hk/</a><br />\n<br />\n(對唔住，咁危難時刻下我知而家仲叫大家課金可能好反感，但我相信兄弟爬山，各有各做，行得通就全力去做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)"},{"pid":"f2e6ebc3ae9bb1bf02bc0b3e3b5b78a5314ceb73","tid":1725530,"uid":229886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T10:27:38.000Z","msg":"做文宣囉"},{"pid":"177e055f0e3766f3cf0f4d852aedec4adbc4c28c","tid":1725530,"uid":239510,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T10:30:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />文宣光復日"}]}